<DOCNO> LA010894-0050 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 002052 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 8, 1994, Saturday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 9; Column 1; Metro Desk 
