<P>
 Dolores (Val) Rains, a member of the Pleasant Valley school board, has been 
elected to the board of directors of the statewide California School Boards 
Assn. 
</P>
<P>
 Rains, 61, will represent school districts in Ventura, Santa Barbara and San 
Luis Obispo counties on the 24-member board, according to Sherry Jean Cole, a 
spokeswoman for the Pleasant Valley School District. 
</P>
