it was not enough in a Valley Pac-8 Conference game. 
</P>
<P>
 Damon Ollie had 26 points and 17 rebounds for North Hollywood (7-5, 2-0) and 
Fantasia Johnson added 16 points and 11 assists. 
</P>
<P>
 Dante Cain added 19 points for Monroe (3-9, 1-2). 
</P>
<P>
 Sylmar 73, Sherman Oaks CES 54 -- Michael Farmer had 23 points and nine 
assists and Joe Guerra 18 points, all on three-point shots, for the Spartans 
(8-2, 3-0 in the Valley Pac-8 Conference). 
