<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 8, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 2; Foreign Desk 
