 Israel released 101 Palestinian prisoners Friday as a goodwill gesture ahead 
of the resumption of talks with the PLO. 
</P>
<P>
 A government official said the delay in implementing Palestinian self-rule in 
the occupied Gaza Strip and the West Bank city of Jericho was eroding support 
for the peace accord with the Palestine Liberation Organization. 
</P>
