<P>
 Posner Quits 2 Companies: Victor Posner, the Miami investor banned from 
controlling public companies due to numerous securities laws violations, 
resigned in accordance with terms of a Dec. 1 federal court order.He stepped 
down as director and chief executive of Salem Corp., a Pittsburgh-based 
