<P>
 New television movies will highlight the weekend's viewing schedule. 
</P>
<P>
 Neil Patrick Harris and Kelli Williams star Sunday night at 9 on CBS in the 
true-story drama "Snowbound: The Jim and Jennifer Stolpa Story," which revolves 
around the San Francisco couple who, along with their 5-month-old son, were 
stranded for eight days in the snowy Nevada wilderness. 
