<HEADLINE>
<P>
ELSEWHERE; PRO FOOTBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 DENVER BRONCOS vs. RAIDERS 
</P>
<P>
 NFL Playoffs, First Round 
</P>
<P>
 * When: Sunday, 1 p.m. * Site: Coliseum. * Radio: KFI (640). 
</P>
<P>
 Blackout Looming for Sunday's Game 
</P>
<P>
 The Raiders' playoff game with Denver wasn't close to a sellout Friday night, 
but an exact number of remaining tickets was not available, according to Raider 
executive assistant Al LoCasale. There were 14,000 unsold tickets Thursday 
afternoon. 
</P>
<P>
 If Sunday's game does not sell out by 1 p.m. today, it will be blacked out in 
Los Angeles. 
</P>
